* hashie    1\.2\.0    3\.4\.6   = 1\.2\.0    default
* headless  2\.2\.3    2\.3\.1   = 2\.2\.3    test
.fi
.IP "" 0
.P
\fB\-\-filter\-major\fR would only show:
